@node "Document_3" ""
                                 Versions

Version 3.0 - Enhanced features.

            - Adds total time spent online to log file.

            - Each log save will be appended together for convenience.

            - New options to View and delete Balance.log file
              from IBB for convenience.

            - Indicator showing user how much time is being spent online.

            - Added indicator for Rate.

            - Improved Graphical interface.

            - See IBB.pic for V 3.0 preveview.


Version 2.0 - Added Multiple windows support by binding external Decks.

            - Added user configurable rate charge for canadian funds.
              not sure if it will work with other currencies.

            - Bug fixed in timer. Now more precise

            - Now keeps track of Time loged on and off
              in a log file.

            - Saves a Log file of current 'Call'.

            - Released as "Giftware". Register to recieve updates..

            - Log file VIEW enabled (Bonus)

            - fully useable.




Version 0.8 Beta - Windows cannot appear all at once.




@endnode

@node "Document_4" ""
                              Requirements
                              ~~~~~~~~~~~~

                    - Required Cando.library in libs:

                    - Battery backed up clock recomended

                    - An INTERNET account!

                    - Should work fine in 640x200

                    - Aweseome Look in 640x400 (Well at least V3.0!)



@endnode

@node "Document_5" ""
                               Installation
                               ~~~~~~~~~~~~

Unpack IBB.lha to desired location.

Files:

Libs (dir)
    - Cando.library
log  (dir)
    - (Empty) var
var  (dir)
    - rate1.var
    - rate2.var
    - rate3.var
fonts - Xen.font
      - Xen 9dir)
                  -8
                  -9
                  -13

IBB_2.0                <- IBB V2.0
IBB_2.0.info
IBB_3.0_Demo           <- Demo Version of IBB VV3.0
IBB_3.0_Demo.info
IBB_3.0_demo.txt       <- Demo Restrictions
IBB_3.0_demo.txt.info
IBB.Guide              <- IBB v2.0/3.0 docs in AmigaGude format.
IBB.Guide.info
IBB.doc                <- IBB v2.0/3.0 docs in Ascii format.
IBB.doc.info
IBB.pic                <- Preview of IBB V3.0
Register.form


Copy cando.library to LIBS:

Copy IBB:fonts to FONTS: 

Assign IBB: to the Dir where IBB program is located.



@endnode

